function set_window_scale(scale: Number(gint)): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for gdk_x11_display_set_window_scale()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Forces a specific window scale for all windows on this display,
instead of using the default or user configured scale. This
is can be used to disable scaling support by setting <code>scale</code> to
1, or to programmatically set the window scale.</p>  <p>Once the scale is set by this call it will not change in response
to later user configuration changes.</p>
  <p>Since 3.10</p>
